  <Team
    name="Social Entrepreneur Support"
    description="Our team are based across the UK in England, Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland and we work directly with social entrepreneurs delivering support through one to one coaching and enabling peer to peer connections. We aim to find, fund and support those from start up to scale up with the most potential for impact tackling todays biggest challenges including our impact areas of healthy ageing and access to employment. We are committed to equity, diversity, inclusion and belonging."
