    name="Delivery and Investment"
    description="Designing and delivering market-leading support with and alongside our partners, supporters and colleagues. We are focussed on breaking down the barriers faced by social entrepreneurs. This includes accessing specialist expertise through our partnership work, and accessing the right investment through the Growth Impact Fund."
